Installing the card into the server and the game:
On the server: To throw zm_amongus_two_winter.bsp file on the path D: \ ServerCSS \ cstrike \ maps
In the game: To throw zm_amongus_two_winter.bsp file on the path D: \ Games \ CS: S \ cstrike \ maps
Even if you add a server to a file mapcycle.txt maplist.txt votemaplist.txt to register the name card zm_amongus_two_winter
